
# 🌱 Plant Pulse API

## 📌 Overview

Plant Pulse is an AI-powered plant disease detection system specialized in
detecting diseases in lettuce plants.

The system allows users to upload images of lettuce leaves and receive an
accurate prediction of whether the plant is healthy or affected by a disease.

The project consists of:

- Backend REST API built with Node.js and Express.js
- Flutter mobile application
- Frontend React
- AI-based image classification model for lettuce disease detection

The main goal of Plant Pulse is to help farmers and users detect lettuce
diseases early and support better crop management.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ✨ Features

### 👤 User Management
- User registration and login
- Secure authentication using JWT
- Google Sign-In support
- Update profile information
- Upload profile image
- Delete account

### 🌿 Plant Disease Detection
- Upload lettuce leaf images
- AI-based disease prediction
- Detect whether the lettuce is:
  - Healthy
  - botrytis_gray_mold
  - downy_mildew
  - pythium_root_rot
  - tip_burn
  - Not_Lettuce

### 📊 Scan Management
- Save user scan history
- View previous scans
- Track prediction results
- Each user can access only their own scans
 
### ☁️ Cloud Services
- Store profile images and Scan images using Cloudinary
- MongoDB Atlas database

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🛠 Technologies

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB Atlas
